  <brief_title>First Line Comparative Study of EN3348 (MCC) vs BCG in NMIBC</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Double-blind, Multi-center Study Comparing MCC to BCG as First Line Immunotherapy in Patients With Non-muscle Invasive (Superficial) Bladder Cancer at High Risk of Recurrence or Progression</official_title>
  <sponsors>
