  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the safety and efficacy of EN3348 (MCC) versus BCG as
      first line treatment in patients with non-muscle invasive bladder cancer that are at high
      risk for recurrence or progression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
